{"id": "art-1112", "label": "Art. 1112", "title": "Art. 1112: Prezumţia de renunţare", "slug": "art-1112", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1190612309\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1121\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1190612309\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 1112:\nPrezum&#355;ia de renun&#355;are </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1994239178\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1120\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1994239178\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Este prezumat, pân&#259; la proba contrar&#259;, c&#259;\na renun&#355;at la mo&#351;tenire succesibilul care, de&#351;i cuno&#351;tea\ndeschiderea mo&#351;tenirii &#351;i calitatea lui de succesibil, nu &#351;i-a\nexercitat dreptul de op&#355;iune succesoral&#259;, prin acceptarea\nmo&#351;tenirii sau renun&#355;area expres&#259; la mo&#351;tenire, în termenul\nde un an prev&#259;zut la art. 1.103.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_874211924\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1119\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_874211924\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Prezum&#355;ia de renun&#355;are opereaz&#259;,\ndup&#259; împlinirea termenului de un an de la deschiderea mo&#351;tenirii,\ndac&#259; succesibilul, citat în condi&#355;iile legii, nu face dovada\nexercit&#259;rii dreptului de op&#355;iune succesoral&#259;. Cita&#355;ia\ntrebuie s&#259; cuprind&#259;, sub sanc&#355;iunea nulit&#259;&#355;ii\nacesteia, pe lâng&#259; elementele prev&#259;zute de </span><span\nstyle='color:#1B1B1B'>Codul de procedur&#259; civil&#259;</span><span\nstyle='color:black'>, &#351;i precizarea c&#259;, dac&#259; succesibilul nu\n&#351;i-a exercitat dreptul de a accepta mo&#351;tenirea în termenul de\ndec&#259;dere prev&#259;zut la art. 1.103, este prezumat c&#259;\nrenun&#355;&#259; la mo&#351;tenire.</span><br style='mso-special-character:\nline-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}